data.description: OPEN HOUSE: Sunday, Feb. 4th 2023     Don't miss this fantastic opportunity to own a very lovely and well-maintained home just minutes from schools, shopping, the library, and I-5 access. This great 1,595 square foot home features a comfortable layout with a cozy wood burning fireplace in the inviting living room and beautifully crafted cabinets, an island, range, and dining area in the spacious kitchen. 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms down the hall provide plenty of space and storage. Both bathrooms have newer paint and flooring.Outside, you'll appreciate the low maintenance yards with xeriscaping, covered back patio, and deck, RV parking, and large 2 car garage. Recently replaced the heat pump/gas hybrid furnace, electric water heater, garage door opener, ducting, and insulation under the home, making it even hotter in the winter months. The roof is only around 14 years old. This wonderful home won't last long, schedule your showing today!
